### Trigger Drive-folder provisioning for an existing user.
### Replace `1` with an existing user.index from the DB.
POST http://localhost:3000/auth/dev/drive/create-folder/6

###

### Auto-provision via signup flow: create a brand-new user and confirm that
### `drive_folder_id` is filled in the DB.
### Bump the email / firebaseId / id between runs to avoid collisions.
POST http://localhost:3000/auth/signup
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "personal": {
    "fName": "Drive",
    "lName": "Test",
    "id": "999000001",
    "dateOfBirth": "1990-01-01",
    "phone": "0500000001",
    "email": "drive-test-001@example.com",
    "city": "Tel Aviv",
    "firebaseId": "drive-test-uid-001"
  }
}

###

### Sync a (user, business, month) folder → downloads new files, runs Claude OCR,
### stores rows in `extracted_document`. Replace <BUSINESS_NUMBER> with the
### Israeli business / tax id you provisioned the business under.
POST http://localhost:3000/documents/sync/6/<BUSINESS_NUMBER>/2026-05

###

### List extracted rows for that (user, business, month).
GET http://localhost:3000/documents/6/<BUSINESS_NUMBER>/2026-05
